text: Gustavo Guglielmone (born 16 May 1971) is an Argentine former cyclist. He competed in the team pursuit at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Argentine male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Argentina Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
